  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicentre, multinational, prospective observational investigation on ICU
      critically ill patients affected by nosocomial pneumonia, defined as: Out of ICU
      Hospital-acquired Pneumonia (HAP), Non-ventilator ICU-acquired Pneumonia (NV ICUAP),
      Ventilator associated pneumonia (VAP) Ventilator associated tracheobronchitis (VAT).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
